  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p598336/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201404/9c7d425f9c0648a896a5882e0c7b7500.png\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial;\">沪江小编：</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">very good, very beautiful, very...&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">每次表达强烈语气时，还在使用very？作家们发话了，very这个词是词汇匮乏和懒惰的表现！小编为你整理45个&ldquo;高大上&rdquo;单词，下次说英语时不要总说very啦！</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>作家们是这样吐槽very的：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Mark Twain：</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Substitute &lsquo;damn&rsquo; every time you&rsquo;re inclined to write &lsquo;very;&rsquo; your editor will delete it and the writing will be just as it should be.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">马克&middot;吐温：</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">每次想要用very的时候就用damn代替吧；你的编辑会直接帮你删掉它，这样文章才是它该有的样子。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Florence King:&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">'Very' is the most useless word in the English language and can always come out. More than useless, it is treacherous because it invariably weakens what it is intended to strengthen.</span><strong>弗罗伦斯&middot;金：</strong>very是英文中最没用的单词，但又总是会出现。比起无用，它简直就是个隐患，因为它总会削弱你想强调的那个词。</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">N.H. Kleinbaum：</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">So avoid using the word &lsquo;very&rsquo; because it&rsquo;s lazy. Don&rsquo;t use very sad, use morose. Language was invented for one reason, boys - to woo women - and, in that endeavor, laziness will not do.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"><strong>N&middot;H&middot;克莱伯姆</strong><strong>：</strong>不要使用very这个词，因为用它就是偷懒。用morose代替very sad。语言的作用只有一个，小子们，就是用来哄女孩的。如果偷懒的话，怎么哄得到！</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><span style=\"color: #f00;\">45个单词摆脱very：</span>当你想在黑色的词（见下表）前加上very时，请用红色的词代替，不要再用very啦。</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201404/9caf230737f546c897da1ee33f06847c.jpg\" /></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p598336/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p598336\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p597887/\">外媒看中国：文章婚外情事件创微博记录</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p598223/\">囧研究：脸长的男人智商高 卷福你赢了！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p597599/\">英语口语入门：词汇量激增10倍的秘诀！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p597861/\">彭丽媛访欧用国产手机拍照 网友点赞</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p596943/\">又迟到了？学习超级准时的人们的7个习惯</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p598190/\">特别的婚礼：11岁女儿牵手患癌父亲步入礼堂</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p598226/\">911接线员上班首日接自家急救电话 救父一命</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p598249/\">《Let It Go》25种语言版现场录制MV发布</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p595724/\">零基础英语资源分享：给学习找点乐子</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://